immunizationUtils.getMaxDoseSequence(input)==args['doseSequence'] || (args['doseSequence']==1 && immunizationUtils.getMaxDoseSequence(input)==0 && input.isNotGiven())
output.setValue(args['dataElement'], codeUtils.getMappedValueSetCode(args['codeSetCode'], input.hasValueCodeableConcept() ? input.getValueCodeableConcept() : null)); true

context.createReference(trackedEntityInstance.organizationUnitId, 'ID')
dateTimeUtils.getPreciseDate(input.hasOccurrence() ? input.getOccurrence() : null)
